<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Kontakt & Reiseanfrage</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f3;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .form-wrap {
      max-width: 660px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e0ddd6;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    }

    .form-header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0ddd6;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .form-header h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .form-header p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #888;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .form-section { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

    .row { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .row-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .row-3 { grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr 1fr; }

    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }

    .field label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .req { color: #a32d2d; }

    .field input,
    .field select,
    .field textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #d0cec7;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      appearance: auto;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field select:focus,
    .field textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #185fa5;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(24, 95, 165, 0.12);
    }

    .field textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 110px; }

    .error-msg {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #a32d2d;
      display: none;
    }

    .field.has-error input,
    .field.has-error select,
    .field.has-error textarea { border-color: #a32d2d; }

    .field.has-error .error-msg { display: block; }

    /* Flight option cards */
    .flight-options-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .flight-option {
      border: 1px solid #d0cec7;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      background: #fff;
      text-align: left;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .flight-option:hover { border-color: #185fa5; background: #f0f6fc; }

    .flight-option.selected {
      border-color: #185fa5;
      background: #edf4fb;
    }

    .flight-option .opt-icon {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .flight-option .opt-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .flight-option.selected .opt-title { color: #0c447c; }

    .flight-option .opt-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Airport panel */
    .airport-panel {
      background: #f9f8f6;
      border: 1px solid #e0ddd6;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      display: none;
    }

    .airport-panel.visible { display: block; }

    .airport-hint {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .airport-search-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .airport-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }

    .airport-field label { font-size: 14px; color: #1a1a1a; }

    .airport-dropdown { position: relative; }

    .airport-field input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #d0cec7;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
    }

    .airport-field input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #185fa5;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(24, 95, 165, 0.12);
    }

    .airport-list {
      position: absolute;
      top: calc(100% + 4px);
      left: 0; right: 0;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #d0cec7;
      border-radius: 8px;
      z-index: 200;
      max-height: 230px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      display: none;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .airport-list.open { display: block; }

    .airport-item {
      padding: 9px 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ede8;
    }

    .airport-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .airport-item:hover { background: #f0f6fc; }

    .airport-item .code {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #185fa5;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    .airport-item .loc {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .airport-selected {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #185fa5;
      margin-top: 3px;
      min-height: 16px;
    }

    /* Consent */
    .consent-block {
      background: #f9f8f6;
      border: 1px solid #e0ddd6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .consent-block input[type="checkbox"] {
      width: 17px;
      height: 17px;
      margin-top: 3px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      accent-color: #185fa5;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .consent-block p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    #consent-error {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #a32d2d;
      margin-top: 5px;
      display: none;
    }

    /* Submit */
    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 13px;
      background: #185fa5;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover { background: #0c447c; }
    .submit-btn:disabled { background: #9bb3cc; cursor: not-allowed; }

    /* Spinner */
    .spinner {
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      border-top-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: spin 0.7s linear infinite;
      display: none;
    }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    /* Error banner */
    .error-banner {
      background: #fdf2f2;
      border: 1px solid #f0c0c0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #a32d2d;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      display: none;
    }

    /* Success */
    .success-screen {
      display: none;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .success-icon {
      font-size: 52px;
      color: #0f6e56;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .success-screen h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .success-screen p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    @media (max-width: 540px) {
      .row-2, .row-3, .flight-options-grid, .airport-search-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .form-wrap { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="form-wrap">
  <div id="mainForm">

    <div class="form-header">
      <h1>✈ Kontakt &amp; Reiseanfrage</h1>
      <p>Füllen Sie das Formular aus – wir erstellen Ihnen umgehend ein verbindliches Angebot.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Persönliche Angaben -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-label">Persönliche Angaben</div>
      <div class="row row-3" style="margin-bottom:12px">
        <div class="field" id="f-gender">
          <label>Anrede <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <select id="gender">
            <option value="">– wählen –</option>
            <option>Herr</option>
            <option>Frau</option>
            <option>Divers</option>
          </select>
          <span class="error-msg">Bitte wählen Sie eine Anrede.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field" id="f-firstname">
          <label>Vorname <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="firstname" placeholder="Max">
          <span class="error-msg">Bitte geben Sie Ihren Vornamen ein.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field" id="f-lastname">
          <label>Nachname <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="lastname" placeholder="Mustermann">
          <span class="error-msg">Bitte geben Sie Ihren Nachnamen ein.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row row-2">
        <div class="field" id="f-email">
          <label>E-Mail-Adresse <span class="req">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="max@beispiel.de">
          <span class="error-msg">Bitte geben Sie eine gültige E-Mail-Adresse ein.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label>Telefonnummer</label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="+49 123 456789">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nachricht -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-label">Ihre Nachricht</div>
      <div class="field" id="f-message">
        <label>Nachricht <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <textarea id="message" placeholder="Beschreiben Sie Ihr Reiseanliegen..."></textarea>
        <span class="error-msg">Bitte geben Sie eine Nachricht ein.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Flugwunsch -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-label">Flugwunsch</div>
      <div class="flight-options-grid">
        <button type="button" class="flight-option" id="opt-agency" onclick="selectFlight('agency')">
          <div class="opt-icon">💼</div>
          <div class="opt-title">Durch den Reiseexperten buchen lassen</div>
          <div class="opt-sub">Unser Team übernimmt die komplette Flugbuchung für Sie – persönlich und zuverlässig.</div>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="flight-option" id="opt-self" onclick="selectFlight('self')">
          <div class="opt-icon">💻</div>
          <div class="opt-title">Eigenständige Buchung</div>
          <div class="opt-sub">Sie buchen Ihren Flug selbst – wir beraten Sie gerne bei der Auswahl.</div>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="airport-panel" id="airportPanel">
        <div class="airport-hint">Bitte geben Sie Ihre gewünschten Flughäfen an:</div>
        <div class="airport-search-row">
          <div class="airport-field">
            <label>Abflughafen <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="airport-dropdown">
              <input type="text" id="depInput" placeholder="Stadt, Flughafen oder IATA/ICAO…"
                autocomplete="off" oninput="filterAirports('dep')"
                onfocus="openList('dep')" onblur="closeList('dep',300)">
              <div class="airport-list" id="depList"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="airport-selected" id="depSelected"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="airport-field">
            <label>Ankunftsflughafen <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <div class="airport-dropdown">
              <input type="text" id="arrInput" placeholder="Stadt, Flughafen oder IATA/ICAO…"
                autocomplete="off" oninput="filterAirports('arr')"
                onfocus="openList('arr')" onblur="closeList('arr',300)">
              <div class="airport-list" id="arrList"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="airport-selected" id="arrSelected"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Consent -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-label">Verbindliche Bestätigung</div>
      <div class="consent-block">
        <input type="checkbox" id="consent">
        <p>Ich bestätige, dass ich ein <strong>verbindliches Angebot</strong> erhalten möchte und bin damit einverstanden, dass das Team auf Basis meiner Angaben ein individuelles Reiseangebot für mich erstellt. Mir ist bewusst, dass dieses Angebot verbindlich ist und ich nach Annahme in ein vertragliches Verhältnis eintrete.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="consent-error">Bitte erteilen Sie Ihre Zustimmung, um fortzufahren.</div>
    </div>

    <button class="submit-btn" id="submitBtn" onclick="submitForm()">
      <span id="btnText">Verbindliches Angebot anfordern</span>
      <div class="spinner" id="spinner"></div>
    </button>

    <div class="error-banner" id="errorBanner">
      Es ist ein Fehler beim Senden aufgetreten. Bitte versuchen Sie es erneut oder schreiben Sie uns direkt an
      <a href="mailto:info@travel-reiseagentur.de">info@travel-reiseagentur.de</a>.
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Erfolgsmeldung -->
  <div class="success-screen" id="successScreen">
    <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
    <h2>Vielen Dank für Ihre Anfrage!</h2>
    <p>Ihr Reisewunsch ist bei uns eingegangen und wir freuen uns, für Sie das perfekte Angebot zu schnüren. Unser Team meldet sich in Kürze bei Ihnen – gute Reisen beginnen mit der richtigen Planung!</p>
  </div>
</div>

